    "_values": [
      "The city once shimmered with light… powered by three ancient shards.",
      "Until one night… they were stolen.",
      "Until one night… they were stolen.",
      "Until one night… they were stolen.",
      "Until one night… they were stolen.",
      "And the city fell into darkness.",
      "And the city fell into darkness.",
      "But someone is watching. A keeper of quiet magic… ",
      "But someone is watching. A keeper of quiet magic… ",
      "She won’t wait for light to return. She will bring it back. ",
      "She won’t wait for light to return. She will bring it back. ",
      "She won’t wait for light to return. She will bring it back. ",
      "\"Come with me… let’s bring the light back.\""
    ]
  },
